<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-04-08</DATELINE><TITLE>Bracing for impact with new 4R’s in the COVID-19 pandemic- a provincial thoracic radiation oncology consensus</TITLE><BODY>Abstract As COVID-19 pandemic continues to explode, cancer centers worldwide are trying to adapt and are struggling with this constantly changing scenario. Intending to ensure patient safety and deliver quality care, we sought consensus on the preferred thoracic radiation regimen in a Canadian province with 4 new R’s of COVID era.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>